The next time I am in need to rent a vehicle....I AM COMING TO THIS ENTERPRISE!

OK, so let me start by saying I have been renting cars for years, all over the US and Europe.
Let me also say I always have used my debit card as I do not use a major credit card for anything now, its part of my "keep it real and keep it liquid" approach.
That said, renting a car in Arizona is a HUGe pain in the %#!*&!.
I had all but given up when I discovered the SUPER simple, no hassle debit card rental program at the Enterprise location on 44th Street & Thomas Road in Phoenix.
The staff is amazing, fast, efficient, took all my necessary info (you do have to provide some extra proof of income but its painless) and within 15 minutes I was in a great car for the weekend - no problems, no issues just a great group of people looking to make sure I had a good experience renting with Enterprise.
I will always work with this company and always rent from this location while working in Phoenix - its rare to find a hassle-free anything these days and this team is the best ever!

