This place was unreliable and when you need to be at an important occasion, you can't rely on them here.
A man at the hotel the first night had reservations too.
The next morning, he missed his appointment after they told him he was set.
Nice, nice people, but the service left a lot to be desired.
I gave them two stars only due to the girl behind the counter had tried her best.
